    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 for MRL 2 devices. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts hemolysis-relevant quantities within acceptance thresholds across the full COU operating envelope. The model is assessed as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device. No unresolved credibility gaps identified.",
